dockerfile.line: /bin/sh -c apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends 		ca-certificates 		curl 		netbase 		wget 	&& rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
/bin/sh -c set -ex; 	if ! command -v gpg > /dev/null; then 		apt-get update; 		apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends 			gnupg 			dirmngr 		; 		rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*; 	fi
/bin/sh -c apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends 		bzr 		git 		mercurial 		openssh-client 		subversion 				procps 	&& rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
/bin/sh -c apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends 		bzip2 		unzip 		xz-utils 	&& rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

/bin/sh -c { 		echo '#!/bin/sh'; 		echo 'set -e'; 		echo; 		echo 'dirname "$(dirname "$(readlink -f "$(which javac || which java)")")"'; 	} > /usr/local/bin/docker-java-home 	&& chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-java-home

/bin/sh -c set -ex; 		if [ ! -d /usr/share/man/man1 ]; then 		mkdir -p /usr/share/man/man1; 	fi; 		apt-get update; 	apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends 		openjdk-8-jdk="$JAVA_DEBIAN_VERSION" 		ca-certificates-java="$CA_CERTIFICATES_JAVA_VERSION" 	; 	rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*; 		[ "$(readlink -f "$JAVA_HOME")" = "$(docker-java-home)" ]; 		update-alternatives --get-selections | awk -v home="$(readlink -f "$JAVA_HOME")" 'index($3, home) == 1 { $2 = "manual"; print | "update-alternatives --set-selections" }'; 	update-alternatives --query java | grep -q 'Status: manual'

/bin/sh -c #(nop)  LABEL com.metlife.docker.contact=ContainersAndOpenSourceEngineering@metlife.com com.metlife.docker.description=Openjdk 8 JRE com.metlife.docker.dockerfile=https://devtools.metlife.com/bitbucket/projects/MCP/repos/costechnology-openjdk/browse/Dockerfile com.metlife.docker.eaicode=9999 com.metlife.docker.dpccode=XXXX XXXX XXXX com.metlife.docker.license.openjdk=true

/bin/sh -c #(nop)  LABEL com.metlife.docker.contact=gsspframework@metlife.com com.metlife.docker.description=GSSP API Gateway Image with APPDv4.5.7 com.metlife.docker.dockerfile=https://devtools.metlife.com/bitbucket/projects/EAI9498-15/repos/gssp-api-gateway/browse/Dockerfile-appd com.metlife.docker.eaicode=99999 com.metlife.docker.dpccode=XXXX XXXX XXXX com.metlife.docker.license.openjdk=true

|6 APASS=@metlife1 AUSER=deployer branch=feature/init buildNumber=4 commit=0c44da33fcbca24f63131ae1dee3d70713ede12a jarName=gssp-api-gateway /bin/sh -c wget -q -P ${APPD_HOME} --http-user=$AUSER --http-password=$APASS https://devtools.metlife.com/artifactory/ext-release-local/com/metlife/common/AppD/javaagent/${APP_VERSION}/javaagent-${APP_VERSION}.zip && unzip ${APPD_HOME}/javaagent-${APP_VERSION}.zip -d ${APPD_HOME}/ && rm ${APPD_HOME}/javaagent-${APP_VERSION}.zip

|6 APASS=@metlife1 AUSER=deployer branch=feature/init buildNumber=4 commit=0c44da33fcbca24f63131ae1dee3d70713ede12a jarName=gssp-api-gateway /bin/sh -c apt-get update && apt-get install -y vim && apt-get install -y less && apt-get autoremove && apt-get clean 	&& groupadd -g 999 gssp && useradd -r -u 999 -g gssp gsspuser && chown -R gsspuser:gssp /var/log

|6 APASS=@metlife1 AUSER=deployer branch=feature/init buildNumber=4 commit=0c44da33fcbca24f63131ae1dee3d70713ede12a jarName=gssp-api-gateway /bin/sh -c if [ -z $jarName ] || [ -z $commit ] || [ -z $branch ] || [ -z $buildNumber ]; then  echo "\nApplication Docker BUILD FAILED...\n \t Please provide build arguments"; return 1; fi
